been incorporated into the Cepstral products.  These products consist
of the Swift TTS Engine and its associated Language and Lexicon
libraries, the command-line "swift" application, the SwiftTalker MFC
GUI application for Microsoft Windows and Microsoft Windows CE, the
interface to Microsoft SAPI5, the interface to the Apple Macintosh OS
X Speech Manager, and the Cepstral Voice Preferences Pane for Apple
Macintosh OS X.  The license below represent the original source
